original_title: Radio Raps - Laat Ek Jou So Sê
overview: JONATHAN is back for a third time in the much anticipated: LAAT EK JOU SÓ SÊ and this time covers a whole new world of simple tips to live by. After bestsellers LIFE101 and LIFE201, the third live show covers things like going to the beach, moving in with a partner and decorating a house. Don’t miss this hilarious live performance filmed at Carnival City in front of a sold out audience of more than 3000 people. Da vat hy Boys!
title: Radio Raps - Laat Ek Jou So Sê
